==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Infamously
<hw>In"fa*mous*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In an infamous manner or
degree; scandalously; disgracefully; shamefully.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The sealed fountain of royal bounty which had been
<qex>infamously</qex> monopolized and huckstered.</q>
<rj><qau>Burke.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Infamousness</ent>⟦br⟧
